      "writtenOn": "2018-04-02T20:23:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I didn\u0027t write it, but from what I can tell, mixInSimplisiticBlamelist uses BuildSummary queries in order to find the \"previous\" build, so it kind of makes sense to pass in a BuildSummary.\n\nDeriving BuildSummary from the buildbucket build is a much better idea tho.  Adopted.",
