      "writtenOn": "2018-03-26T21:37:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this overwrites finalized properties received from buildbucket.\n\ni think it would be simpler if addXXX functions were renamed to extractXXX and did not make side effects, but instead returned the extracted value to the client. Then the client can decide what to do with it, e.g. conditionally add to the build",
